Package: bottle-imp
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, systemd (>= 232-25), python3 (>= 3.7), python3-pip, systemd-container (>= 232-25)
Description: helper for native systemd support under WSL
 Fixes some secondary facilities and allows easy access to a user session
 when systemd is run under Windows Subsystem for Linux using its native
 support. A spinoff of system-genie.
